<!DOCTYPE html>

<html style = "height:100%;width:100%;margin:0px;">
<head>
  {{> head}}

  <title> WebExhibition - {{title}}</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href = "./dist/css/simple-app.css">
</head>
<body>

	<header>
		<div class="header-content">
			<h1>${header.title}</h1>
			<p class="p-font-400">${header.subTitle}</p>
			<a href="index.html"><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-left" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
		</div>
	</header>

	<nav>
		<h3>抽獎系統</h3>
		<h3>即時問卷系統</h3>
	</nav>

	<section>
		<div class="section-title">
			<h1 class="col-xs-6 col-md-2 col-md-offset-1">目標問題</h1>
		</div>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="section-content col-xs-8 col-xs-offset-2 col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3">
				<p><span class="color-blue p-font-400">舉例：抽獎。</span>
					<br>
				抽籤屬於網路上很基本功能的小程式，但卻因為功能簡單所以普遍上往往完成功能，卻忘了「抽獎」這動作應該要給使用者帶來愉悅的「體驗」。
				</p>

				<p><span class="color-blue p-font-400">舉例：即時問卷系統</span>
					<br>
				以往都是用紙本問卷當作回饋表單，若是想知道回饋結果只能乾等一兩個工作天。我開始思考，能否使用電子表單改善此現象，並呈現即時回饋與分析？
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="section-title">
			<h1 class="col-xs-6 col-md-2 col-md-offset-1">如何思考</h1>
		</div>
		
		<div class="row">
			<div class="section-content col-xs-8 col-xs-offset-2 col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3">
				<ul>
					<li>抽獎的心情是愉悅的、驚喜的，所以畫面也應該要這樣設計。</li>

					<li class="color-blue">拉霸代表自主的掌控，抽卡的方式讓人好像有真的抽出來的感覺。</li>

					<li>填超過3分鐘的問卷有很大機率造成資料的不準確性</li>

					<li class="color-blue">人們總是喜歡立即性的回饋。</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="section-title">
			<h1 class="col-xs-6 col-md-2 col-md-offset-1">專案成果</h1>
		</div>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="section-board col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
				<div id="board-slotMachine" class="board-img" onclick="window.open('https://ncku-ccs.github.io/slotMachine/slot_machine.html');"></div>
				<div class="board-content">
					<h2>神奇抽獎機</h2>
					<p class="color-red-pink">全新體驗的抽獎效果</p>
					<br>
					<div class="link">
						<a href="https://ncku-ccs.github.io/slotMachine/slot_machine.html" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-eye" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
						<a href="https://github.com/NCKU-CCS/slotMachine" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="circle"></div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="section-board col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
				<div id="board-d3ForceSimple" class="board-img" onclick="window.open('https://tsehang.github.io/d3ForceSimple/');"></div>
				<div class="board-content">
					<h2>即時問卷系統</h2>
					<p class="color-red-pink">立即回饋分析的有趣問卷系統</p>
					<br>
					<div class="link">
						<a href="https://tsehang.github.io/d3ForceSimple/" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-eye" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
						<a href="https://github.com/TseHang/d3ForceSimple" target="_blank" ><i class="fa fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="circle"></div>
			</div>
		</div>

	</section>

	<footer class="footer">
		{{> block-footer}}
	</footer>


</body>
<script type="text/javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/vue@2.1.6/dist/vue.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="dist/js/block-simple-app.js"></script>

</html>